-- Reliance to Invest $1 Billion in Aerospace Business, Times Says
-- B y   S i d d h a r t h   P h i l i p
-- 2012-07-28T02:58:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-28/reliance-to-invest-1-billion-in-aerospace-business-times-says.html
Reliance Industries Ltd. (RIL)  will invest
$1 billion “over the next few years” in its aerospace
business, the Economic Times reported, citing company executives
it didn’t identify.  The company will collaborate with global firms to bring
aerospace technology to India, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
